<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>海洋保护 - PPT 演示</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>
        /* 基本页面样式 */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #e0f7fa;
            color: #004d40;
        }
        .slide {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            transition: opacity 0.5s;
        }
        .slide h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .slide p {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            line-height: 1.5;
            max-width: 80%;
        }
        .buttons {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #004d40;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #00796b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="buttons">
    <button class="button" onclick="previousSlide()">上一页</button>
    <button class="button" onclick="nextSlide()">下一页</button>
</div>

<div class="slide" id="slide1">
    <div>
        <h1>海洋保护的重要性</h1>
        <p>海洋覆盖了地球表面70%以上，是地球生命支持系统的关键组成部分。保护海洋意味着保护我们未来的生态系统。</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="slide" id="slide2" style="display: none;">
    <div>
        <h1>海洋污染现状</h1>
        <p>塑料垃圾、化学污染和过度捕捞正对海洋生态造成巨大压力。每年有数百万吨塑料进入海洋，影响着海洋生物的生存。</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="slide" id="slide3" style="display: none;">
    <div>
        <h1>海洋保护的措施</h1>
        <p>建立海洋保护区、减少塑料使用、加强渔业管理以及提高公众意识是保护海洋的有效方法。</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="slide" id="slide4" style="display: none;">
    <div>
        <h1>每个人的责任</h1>
        <p>我们每个人都可以通过减少塑料消费、参与清洁海滩行动以及支持环保政策来为海洋保护贡献力量。</p>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
    let currentSlide = 1;
    const totalSlides = 4;

    function showSlide(slideIndex) {
        for (let i = 1; i <= totalSlides; i++) {
            const slide = document.getElementById('slide' + i);
            slide.style.display = (i === slideIndex) ? 'flex' : 'none';
        }
    }

    function nextSlide() {
        if (currentSlide < totalSlides) {
            currentSlide++;
            showSlide(currentSlide);
        }
    }

    function previousSlide() {
        if (currentSlide > 1) {
            currentSlide--;
            showSlide(currentSlide);
        }
    }

    // Initial display
    showSlide(currentSlide);
</script>

</body>
</html>
